manhattan.firsthandler

クラス SeedSAC

  • java.lang.Object
    • manhattan.firsthandler.SeedSAC
  • すべての実装されたインタフェース:
    java.lang.Runnable

    class SeedSAC
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
    Class for extracting a seed file. It creates SAC files from the seed file. This class assumes that rdseed, evalresp and sac exists in your PATH. The software can be found in IRIS.
    バージョン:
    0.1.8
    作成者:
    kensuke

      • SeedSAC

        SeedSAC(java.nio.file.Path seedPath,
        java.nio.file.Path outputDirectoryPath)
 throws java.io.IOException
        パラメータ:
        seedPath - to be extracted from
        outputDirectoryPath - Path where extracted files are placed
        例外:
        java.io.IOException - if the outputDirectoryPath already has events which also exists in the seed file or an error occurs

      • SeedSAC

        SeedSAC(java.nio.file.Path seedPath,
        java.nio.file.Path outputDirectoryPath,
        GlobalCMTID id)
 throws java.io.IOException
        解凍するseed file
        パラメータ:
        seedPath - 解凍するseedファイル
        outputDirectoryPath - inside this folder, the seed file is extracted. If the folder does not exist, it will be created.
        id - global cmt id
        例外:
        java.io.IOException - If the folder already has event folders which also exists in the seed file.
